column1: #Text=The 1994 settlement agreement between UNIX Systems Laboratories (USL) and Regent of University of California (USL v.
#Text=BSDi) was unsealed in November 2004 under the California Public Records Act (California Code ยง 6250-6270).
#Text=The details of the settlement may have ramifications with respect to the SCO v.
#Text=IBM case with SCO believing it is the successor in interest to USL.
